{"flatpakAppId":"com.play0ad.zeroad","name":"0 A.D.","summary":"Real-Time Strategy Game of Ancient Warfare","description":"\n    <p>\n      0 A.D. is a real-time strategy (RTS) game of ancient warfare.\n      It's a historically-based war/economy game that allows players to relive\n      or rewrite the history of thirteen ancient civilizations, each depicted\n      at their peak of economic growth and military prowess.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      The thirteen factions are: Three of the Hellenic States (Athens, Sparta and\n      Macedonia), two of the kingdoms of Alexander the Great's successors\n      (Seleucids and Ptolemaic Egyptians), two Celtic tribes (Britons and\n      Gauls), the Romans, the Persians, the Iberians, the Carthaginians, the\n      Mauryas and the Kushites.\n      Each civilization is complete with substantially unique artwork,\n      technologies and civilization bonuses.\n    </p>\n  ","developerName":null,"projectLicense":"GPL-2.0+ and CC-BY-SA","homepageUrl":"https://play0ad.com/","donationUrl":"https://play0ad.com/community/donate/","translateUrl":"https://trac.wildfiregames.com/wiki/Localization","bugtrackerUrl":"https://trac.wildfiregames.com/","helpUrl":null,"categories":[{"name":"Game"},{"name":"StrategyGame"}],"downloadFlatpakRefUrl":"0ad","currentReleaseVersion":null,"currentReleaseDescription":null,"iconDesktopUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/com/play0ad/zeroad/57835afd3aeba08ea6de0466c5d5becf/icons/128x128/0ad_0ad.png","iconMobileUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/com/play0ad/zeroad/57835afd3aeba08ea6de0466c5d5becf/icons/128x128/0ad_0ad.png","screenshots":[{"thumbUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/com/play0ad/zeroad/57835afd3aeba08ea6de0466c5d5becf/screenshots/image-1_224x126.png","imgMobileUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/com/play0ad/zeroad/57835afd3aeba08ea6de0466c5d5becf/screenshots/image-1_1248x702.png","imgDesktopUrl":"https://appstream.ubuntu.com/media/noble/com/play0ad/zeroad/5